<br>
However:<br>
<br>
Most large races can bash (slam) to get aggro and interrupt casters without using a shield.  Smaller races and Vah Shir get a similar ability at level 55+ when their kick gets upgraded.  It can be fiddly fighting small mobs though and you'll need shrink potions to get around in places like Thurg.<br>
<br>
Ogres get the large race slam thing, plus the best tank starting stats and unstunnability from the front (which isn't as great as people say but still can be useful occasionally).<br>
<br>
Some people say small warriors can have problems fighting certain large mobs (I wouldn't know, never played a shorty tank).<br>
