<br>
Ogres start with significantly higher STR than any other race...but, 1 STR = 1 ATK (generally), and very little else. Also, STR gear is incredibly over-abundant, and the stat can be buffed to all hell. Advantage? Nope.<br>
<br>
Also start with higher STA. But, at low levels, stamina does very little. And by higher levels when it matters *GASP* between equipment and buffs, you can get it maxed, or close to it with any race!<br>
<br>
